    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that makes sense. so basically the money just sits there in a middle ground until everything is official? it sounds a bit weird that the money isn't just going straight to the seller right away. is there a risk of the money just getting lost or someone taking it early if there isn't a strict \"guard\" on it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
